TO RUN
------

Install python packges: fastapi, bokeh, uvicorn (pip install -r requirements.txt)
OR activate geojson-layers venv.

Locally:

Run command "uvicorn main:app --reload --port XXXX" and visit http://127.0.0.1:XXXX

Remotely:

On local machine run 'ssh -L XXXX:localhost:YYYY user@remote'

On remote machine run "uvicorn main:app --reload --port YYYY" and visit http://127.0.0.1:XXXX on local

TO VIEW GEOJSON
---------------

.geojson file to be shown is given in get_geojson function in routes/templates.py

Colour scheme defined for each "level" feature property - edit the variable color_legend in static/map.js and make sure there is a hex colour code given for every level in the file. Open developer tools (Ctl+Shift+J in chrome) and view the console to get hints!
